  "description": "<p>Well-versed in retrofitting of Engine and crankshafts within time</p><p>· With enriched experience in troubleshooting of two stroke and four stroke engines</p><p>· Sound knowledge in framing and executing of scheduled maintenance plans, estimates, and contract specifications.</p><p>· Well adapted to Preventive, Conditional based Predictive & Break down maintenance of Engines and plant utilities</p><p>· Laid down SOP’s and MIS reports and have knowledge in implementation of ISO-9001 -2001, 18000 - 2007, 14000 – 2007.</p><p>· Conducted operational and performance tests on marine machinery and equipment on behalf of makers like Hyundai and Yanmar.</p><p>· Prepared technical reports for the final evaluation by regulatory and insurance bodies.</p>",
